Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:17.99,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,PETALS OF REINCARNATION
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.01,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,BAKAT: INCI YANG EKSTREM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:32.71,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,IBITSU NITEN REIHOU - MAYAT SEMBILAN WARNA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.47,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,ENPI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:10.51,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,TSUKIKAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:11.77,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,YAMAKAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:12.89,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,URANAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:14.64,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,UKIFUNE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:15.89,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,SETSUKOU
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.32,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,SANGAKU ZANTEI SETTETSU
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:34.45,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,HANAGURUMA - MYOUSHIN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:35.91,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,ZENTAI - TEBIKI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:37.67,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,RANKEN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:15.98,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 11: BAKAT YANG ROBEK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.24,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,BAKAT\NMALAM YANG MENYEDIHKAN NOCHE TRISTE)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:42.96,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,EROR
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.63,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,MOHON ISI DAYA MOHON KELUARKAN PANAS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:36.37,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,EPISODE 12: SAMPAI SUARANYA TERDENGAR
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, pergi dan kalahkan\Npara Pengembali yang tersesat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun kita belum tahu lokasinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benih Reinkarnasi memang ada!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah memberi tahu\Npihak berwenang terkait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita bergerak juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kenapa begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya kau, Kitazuka, yang ingat\Napa yang terjadi selama satu jam itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemungkinan karena ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mnemonik melukai diri sendiri, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Teknik mnemonik yaitu menghafal sesuatu\Ndengan melukai diri sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski lupa, kau bisa mengingat\Nmelalui luka atau rasa sakit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini metode yang cukup efektif,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa akan ada orang lain selain aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seseorang yang mengingat semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seseorang yang menerima sesuatu\Ndari Pria Tanpa Wajah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau takut?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja tubuhku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa mengendalikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi ayahku...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Demi memulihkan dojo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus mencapai puncak keahlian pedang!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia kerasukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu menghunus pedang\Ndi medan perang hidup atau mati,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau harus bertarung\Ndengan mempertaruhkan nyawamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.09,0:02:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berjuanglah sesukamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan berusaha maksimal\Nuntuk menghadapimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yagyu Shinkage-ryu Seiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Marobashi".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibitsu Niten Reihou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mayat Empat Warna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sini, Bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibitsu Niten Reihou!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mayat Sembilan Warna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menangkisnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari depan juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan coba-coba mendekat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penghalang tekanan yang mematikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pertarungan ketahanan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mendekat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tak mempan pada Nona Yagyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hawa ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jurus pematian instan\Nyang mengabaikan jarak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena logika di baliknya masih belum jelas,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}begitu dia berhasil melakukannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia pasti mati...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hancurlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menembus Pedang Tunggal Baja Murni!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang dilihat Nona Yagyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menghancurkan orang lain
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan menjadikannya batu loncatan,\Ndan hanya ini kemampuanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu hanya trik kasar,\Ntidak layak disebut teknik!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kutunjukkan keahlian pedang\Nyang sesungguhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau bisa pergi dengan tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memotong tanah di kakinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sengaja menggunakan pedangnya\Nuntuk menendang debu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia berusaha\Nmenyembunyikan gerakan kakinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi mereka terlalu jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dia di luar jangkauan serangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menggunakan sinar bulan\Nuntuk menyilaukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak boleh ceroboh\Njika ingin menangkis pedang itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dia tidak bisa\Nmerusak keseimbangan lawannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia akan terpaksa tetap bertahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terburu-buru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga tidak boleh ceroboh\Nsaat mengayunkan pedangmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rentetan yang cair seperti air mengalir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini seperti menonton\Ndemonstrasi seni bela diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meskipun Haito memiliki keuntungan fisik,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia menekannya dari depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kunci dia melakukan itu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah "prediksi" yang sangat tepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Yagyu benar-benar bisa melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sia-sia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inci Ekstrem adalah bakat\Nyang mendorong visi hingga batasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu memungkinkanku secara sadar memicu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"gerakan lambat" yang dialami saat darurat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Digabungkan dengan kendali jarak yang tepat,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}begitu aku bisa mendeteksi lawanku,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bisa mengejar mereka,\Ntapi menyerang lebih dahulu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menghindar dan mengayunkan pedangku\Ndengan kecepatan maksimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengambil nyawa tidak membutuhkan\Ntebasan lebar yang melengkung.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu inci dari ujung
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.09,0:06:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah lebih dari cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pembuluh darah hanya\Nbeberapa milimeter di bawah kulit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Organ hanya tiga sentimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku bisa menyerang titik vital\Ndengan tepat, pertarungan akan berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Pertarungan hidup atau mati\Nditentukan dalam satu inci."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mataku bisa melihat semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tebasan putus asa dan berat\Nyang lahir dari ketidaksabaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia tak bisa membalas atau menangkis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pasti akan kena.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini serangan terakhir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selalu seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan saat aku punya celah jelas\Nuntuk serangan mematikan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia menghindarinya dengan sangat tipis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya "mataku" melemah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Refleks Musashi melampaui manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyebalkan sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak kusangka dia berusaha\Nmencapai puncak keahlian pedang
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}melalui fisik...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Darah merembes di punggungnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa luka sebelumnya terbuka kembali?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan, Haito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa berhenti sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak melawan orang tak bersenjata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pergilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja, Nona Yagyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bilang itu untuk\Nmembangun kembali dojo dan ayahmu, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang sebenarnya kau inginkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bakat yang kau cari...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kekuatan" yang kau incar, apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:08:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai aku mengerti,\Naku akan terus berjuang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar-benar orang yang menyedihkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menemukan kunci untuk Musashi... bukan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}untuk mengembalikan kesadaran Haito.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita mundur sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesimpulannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga minta maaf kepadamu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena melibatkanmu begitu dalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku yakin kau juga menyaksikannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau melihatnya, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sifat asli Kelopak Bunga...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kau membantu\Nmengakhiri para Pengembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Yagyu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita harus turun gunung.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus mencari tempat untuk mengobatimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fokus saja pada Haito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kau bilang begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meyakinkan Haito sepertinya mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kabut hitam apa itu tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu obsesi dengan "kekuatan".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kemungkinan dipicu oleh trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hatinya yang patah bermanifestasi\Ndalam bentuk kelopak bunga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jiwa yang menyedihkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyedihkan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Kekuatan" itu relatif.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama ada lawan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pengejaran "kekuatan" tidak akan berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertarungan akan berlangsung selamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ini sebabnya Haito\Ntetap menjadi Pengembali yang belum lengkap.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Orang yang tidak pernah puas."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk menjadi kuat selamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menjadi Pengembali\Nuntuk mengejar kekuatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bahkan menyakiti ayah tercintanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dia terus berjuang\Nuntuk menjadi lebih kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena takut kehilangan tempatnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu dia tahu ayahnya sudah meninggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pantas saja dia hancur.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kita bisa mengembalikannya\Nke kondisi di mana kita bisa bicara?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan menghancurkan kabut hitam\Ndi sekitar Haito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.33,0:10:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangkis setiap gerakannya\Ndan hancurkan semangatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kita melakukan itu,\Nkabutnya akan menghilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sisanya terserah padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, Nona Yagyu, kau akan bertarung,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan aku yang akan meyakinkannya, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan bertarung.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa mengalahkan Haito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inci Ekstrem memberi tekanan besar\Npada otak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan luka-luka ini,\Naku tidak bisa bertarung lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiga hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam tiga hari tiga malam,\Naku akan mengajarimu cara menghadapinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bicara seolah-olah aku yang bertarung.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku tidak bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini terlalu sulit bagiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yanagi Jusan-dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu "Mayat Berwarna" karya Haito.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau masih berpikir\Naku tidak bisa mengajarimu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menyadarinya dan menciptakannya kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Yagyu sungguh luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tetap tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa pria\Nyang ingin "membasmi Pengembali"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.66,0:11:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak ambisius?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan masalah pola pikir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.91,0:11:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya pria biasa yang biasa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mustahil aku bisa mencapai level Haito\Natau Nona Yagyu dalam semalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika menggunakan senjata\Natau trik tersembunyi, itu satu hal...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tak bisa bertarung tingkat tinggi\Nyang harus menerima seranganmu langsung.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong kosong apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau masih punya lengan kananmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.85,0:12:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan bakatnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku yang membunuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Hei!\N- Menaklukkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian Pengembali yang tersesat, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mengambil Cabang itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Target pertama\Ndalam perburuan Pengembali tersesat,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pengembali "Penakluk".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka telah maju\Nterutama melalui Afrika Utara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesempatan untuk mendapatkan\Ntiga Cabang sekaligus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangan Besi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sembilan orang...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepuluh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:13:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak puas dengan jumlahnya,\Ntapi apa boleh buat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Menaklukkan dengan kekuatan belaka!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mudah dihancurkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu mudah! Tangan Besi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya berjalan sesuai perhitungan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Almagro. Bakat: Requerimiento!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bakat di mana makin banyak musuh,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}makin kuat kemampuan bertarungnya,\Ndan makin banyak persenjataannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, jika jumlah lawan rendah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah kau bilang\Nakan menghancurkanku, Götz?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, senjataku tidak cukup?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}selamat tinggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang barbar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meleset.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Möbius, Carothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan Kotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Giliranku! Kau membuatku tidak sabar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anjing-anjingku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktunya makan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bagus!\N- Bakat Norton diaktifkan dalam...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Cabut tenggorokan mereka!\N- Tiga, dua, satu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahkan penjahat yang seperti binatang buas
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak bisa mengalihkan pandangan\Ndari kejayaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, aku, Norton, akan menjadi lawanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Anjing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perhatian kalian benar-benar lengah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita hampir membatalkan bakat\NKelompok Pelahap milik Pizarro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti prediksi Ponsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bakat para Penakluk adalah tipe\Nyang menargetkan banyak musuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak akan membantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Mesmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katakan sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bakat kami bertiga bukan tipe petarung.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di lingkungan ini, aku hampir tidak berguna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dalam hal kekuatan menyerang,\Nini seharusnya cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kembalilah, anjing-anjingku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa pun perintahku,\Nanjing-anjing itu tidak mau mendengarkanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan serangan yang monoton\Ndan tidak berubah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka meremehkan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berbalik.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap ini berjalan lancar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tampak tidak puas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau berpikir,\N"Aku bisa membunuh mereka dalam sekejap"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perpindahan Ruang-mu\Nmemang kuat dalam pertempuran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.25,0:15:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kita juga perlu menguji kecenderungan\Ndan bakat para Pengembali yang mendukung.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelihatannya akan segera berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ujian, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini gawat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo mundur sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cari kota tempat kita bisa menyeret\Nbanyak warga sipil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cortés...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malam ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertikaian internal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Bukan itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.66,0:15:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanda termal berat di mana-mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka memperluas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mundur ke Titik B!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.00,0:16:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menaklukkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wahai malam,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}biarkan semua hal meleleh\Nmenjadi kegelapan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanda termal menurun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menyerang sebelum bakatnya aktif.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang diharapkan dari Einstein,\Npengalaman tempurnya membuat perbedaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rekaman video selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, lanjutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertempuran sudah berakhir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kenapa suasananya berat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita berdua kesulitan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia diperintah begitu Gale tertidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Markas kehabisan daya karena itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membuat Ahli Komputer bekerja\Nmelampaui batas, dan Perhitungan Prediksi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pada dasarnya menjadi prekognisi seketika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Edison.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Isi dayanya nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buka gudang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya Albert akan mengamuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Ein. Kau menjatuhkan cabangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan terlalu memaksakan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya melamun sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.11,0:17:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakiku terasa sangat lemah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan mataku perih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perpindahan Ruang...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.71,0:17:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu berat untuk tubuh ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.42,0:17:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tampak pucat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, ayo kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita hubungi\Nunit penjaga belakang Kitazuka dahulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Data koordinat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu semacam alat pendukung?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kau kehilangan satu kaki...\Nkau sulit bergerak, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari mana asal orang ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dia tahu soal kakiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang ini berbahaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menutup jarak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.42,0:18:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang ini tahu bakatku...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lemah sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kekuatan menyerang Perpindahan Ruang-mu
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hanyalah produk sampingan\Ndari retakan spasial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya perlu menjauh dari perbatasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampah seperti ini\Nmenyebut dirinya Einstein?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar-benar menyebalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak tahu diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau membuatku muak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lupa memperkenalkan diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Albert Einstein dari Hutan Para Legenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.34,0:18:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Newton.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Newton...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana rasanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditaklukkan oleh mantan rekanmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.98,0:19:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sakit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apel bodoh! Bangunlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lepaskan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kau lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangkap orang itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apel Kecil, bukankah Nightingale\Nsudah memberitahumu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau harus "membela diri".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Newton...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.75,0:19:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bangunlah, kumohon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhentilah menyakiti dirimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangan Besi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku meleset?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana mungkin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jangan mengganggu kesenangan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar monyet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka berteleportasi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan mereka melayang di udara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:19:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang tadi itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perpindahan Ruang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah aku baru saja menjawabmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Einstein dari Hutan Para Legenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa ada dua Einstein?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenanglah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku datang untuk bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bicara?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menyerang kami lebih dahulu,\Nlalu ingin bicara?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.05,0:20:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lelucon ada batasnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlalu dramatis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku mau,\Nkalian semua pasti sudah mati sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, dengarkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian ingin menghentikan\NHutan Para Legenda, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini, Hutan Para Legenda adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}organisasi Pengembali terbesar dan terkuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penuh dengan banyak kepribadian\NKelas Legenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan masing-masing dari mereka\Nmemiliki bakat manusia super.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena kau tidak bisa menghadapi mereka\Nsecara langsung,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau berencana menggunakan Benih\Nuntuk penghancuran bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu keputusan yang sangat bijaksana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi Hutan Para Legenda saat ini berada\Ndi bawah kendali Nightingale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu-satunya pengecualian\Nadalah aku dan Tesla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan Nightingale itu saat ini tidak aktif.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena tuan mereka tertidur,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.14,0:21:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}para Pengembali yang tunduk padanya\Njuga menghentikan semua aktivitas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nightingale benar-benar\Ntidak berdaya sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesempatan yang sempurna!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi lokasinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau akan bilang,\N"Kau tak tahu lokasinya," kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.07,0:21:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itulah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan kuberi tahu koordinat markas kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau mengalahkan Nightingale,\Npara Pengembali lain akan kembali normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tentu saja, Newton kesayanganmu juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa tujuanmu memberi tahu kami semua ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku punya satu syarat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yaitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Setidaknya lukai aku sekali."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, mari kita mulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, aku akan pemanasan dengan mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah itu selesai,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan bermain denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai suaranya terdengar.
